{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_04_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 1話 こっそりストーキング",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は夏フェスに出演するLizNoirの）\n（付き添いでビーチに来たんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today‚ I came to the beach as a companion for LizNoir‚ ）\n（who is performing at the summer festival…But now…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 6.1364401818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、かき氷です\n{user}さん、あーんして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ have some shaved ice.\nCome on‚ {user}-san‚ say \"ahh.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、一人で食べられるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ it's fine. I can eat it by myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.38478508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.7812249821
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ～、照れてるんですかぁ？\n恥ずかしがらなくていいんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Are you feeling shy?\nYou don't have to be embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり夏と言えばかき氷ですよね\nメロン味のかき氷、甘くて冷たくて美味しいですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to summer‚ it's definitely shaved ice‚ right~?\nThis melon-flavored shaved ice is sweet‚ cold‚ and delicious~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 34.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "溶けちゃう前にこころが食べさせてあげますね\nお口を開けて……はい、あーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro will feed it to you before it melts.\nOpen your mouth… There you go‚ \"ahh~\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（まいったな……どうしてこんなことに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm in trouble… How did I end up in this situation…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時間は遡って、夏フェスの数週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Go back in time‚ a few weeks before the summer festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 46.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの四人で沖縄に行きたいので\nスケジュールの調整をお願いしま～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go to Okinawa with the four members of LizNoir‚\nso I'll ask for the schedule to be adjusted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄って……\n莉央さんと葵は新曲作りで忙しいんじゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okinawa…\nAren't Rio-san and Aoi busy with creating a new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "その曲作りで行き詰まってるから\n気持ちを切り替えるために合宿するんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're stuck in a rut with that song creation‚\nso we're going for a training camp to change their mindset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "合宿だったら沖縄じゃなくてもいいだろ\n行き先が夏の沖縄なんて遊ぶ気まんまんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's a training camp‚ it doesn't have to be in Okinawa‚ right?\nGoing to Okinawa in the summer seems like you just want to have fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってないですね～\nいい曲を作るために、夏の沖縄に行くんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't understand at all.\nWe're going to Okinawa to create a good song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんはデビューしてすぐ人気になったから\n今まで海で遊ぶ暇がなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and Aoi-san became popular right after their debut‚\nso they haven't had time to play at the beach until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "海で遊んだ経験がないのに\n夏の曲なんて作れる訳ないじゃないですかぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without any experience of playing at the beach‚\nhow can they create a summer song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "つーまーりー、夏の曲を作るためには\nまず夏の海を満喫する必要があるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ in order to create a summer song‚\nthey need to fully enjoy the summer at the beach first!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "「新曲を書かないと、ツアーが出来ないわ！\nそのためには気高く沖縄で合宿するしかないのよっ」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"We need to write a new song to have a tour!\"\n\"To do that‚ we must proudly go on a training camp in Okinawa!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "……って莉央さんも言ってました～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rio-san said that too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（いや、それは絶対に嘘だろう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（No‚ that's definitely a lie…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも確かに、沖縄の夏を体験することは\n難航している曲作りのヒントになるかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I guess experiencing Okinawa's summer\nmight be a hint for overcoming the difficult songwriting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "そう思いますよね？\nだから、スケジュールの調整をお願いしま～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you'd say that.\nSo‚ please adjust the schedule for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。みんなで沖縄へ行けるように調整するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I'll make arrangements so that everyone can go to Okinawa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n持つべきものはチョロいマネージャーさんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nWhat a nice easygoing manager~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "チョロいって……まぁいいか。それじゃあ俺も\n一緒に行けるように仕事を片付けておかないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Easygoing… well‚ never mind.\nIn that case‚ I'll need to finish my work so I can go with you guys.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　{user}さんも\n沖縄について来る気なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? {user}-san‚\nare you planning to come to Okinawa too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "旅費さえ出してくれたら、{user}さんは\nいなくてもいいんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to be there {user}-san‚\njust pay us the travel expenses…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん以外は未成年なんだから\n大人が同行した方がいいだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since everyone else is a minor except Rio-san‚\nhaving an adult accompany you would be better‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "保護者なら莉央さんがいるから大丈夫ですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rio-san is there as our guardian‚ so it's fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "でも葵と愛とこころの面倒を\n莉央さん一人で見るのは大変じゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But taking care of Aoi‚ Ai‚ and Kokoro alone\nmight be tough for Rio-san‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん以外\n全員問題児みたいに言わないで下さーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't talk like\nwe are \"problem children\" besides Rio-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "それに、夏の新曲を作るために\nこころ達は沖縄の海を満喫しなくちゃいけないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And besides‚ in order to create a summer song‚\nKokoro and the others need to fully enjoy Okinawa's sea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにマネージャーさんが一緒だったら\n羽を伸ばして遊べないじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if the manager is there‚\nwe won't be able to have fun freely‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱ遊ぶ気まんまんじゃないか……\nだったら、みんなには内緒でついて行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you really just want to have fun…\nIn that case‚ I'll secretly follow you without them noticing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "気付かれないように後をつけて、何かあった時は\nこっそりフォローする。それならいいだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something happens‚\nI'll provide discreet support. Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "……つまり、こころ達をストーキングして\nプライベートの水着姿をこっそり覗き見したいと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So you're saying you want to stalk Kokoro\nand secretly peep at her in a swimsuit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "……盗撮は犯罪ですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Peeping is a crime‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "人聞きの悪いことを言うな\n俺はみんなのことが本気で心配なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't say such a scandalous thing.\nI genuinely care about everyone and want to make sure you're safe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr023.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……そこまで言われちゃったら仕方ないですね\nそれだけ心配してくれてる訳だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… I can't help it if you put it that way.\nSo that's how concerned you are about us. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr024.m4a",
      "text": "邪魔をしないって約束するならついて来てもいいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if you promise not to interfere‚ then you can come along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "約束する、邪魔にならないようにこっそりついて行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I promise. I won't.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr025.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n絶対にバレないようにして下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okieee.\nPlease make sure no one finds out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr026.m4a",
      "text": "それから、いくら水着姿のこころが可愛くても\n盗撮はダメですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ no matter how cute Kokoro looks in a swimsuit‚\nno peeping allowed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr027.m4a",
      "text": "東京に強制送還しちゃいますから～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll have you deported to Tokyo if you do that~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "だからしないって……",
      "translations": {
